104
00:06:32,160 --> 00:06:32,810
Come back!

105
00:06:42,070 --> 00:06:42,580
Come back!

106
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:46,220
Get back here!

107
00:07:13,180 --> 00:07:15,540
[Yellow Maple Valley]

108
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:22,170
A sky full of yellow maple leaves.

109
00:07:23,510 --> 00:07:23,930
Is this

110
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:25,780
Yellow Maple Valley?

111
00:09:36,560 --> 00:09:37,290
What's this?

112
00:09:51,100 --> 00:09:52,700
[Wu Xuan, Liu Jing]

113
00:09:52,800 --> 00:09:54,560
[Song Meng, Zhong Weiniang]

114
00:09:57,160 --> 00:09:57,980
That's

115
00:09:59,510 --> 00:10:00,290
