116
00:10:05,870 --> 00:10:06,540
Fu Yunzi.

117
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:09,370
Remember these tiles?

118
00:10:09,370 --> 00:10:10,000
[Fu Yunzi, Clear Void Sect]

119
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:10,980
Show-off.

120
00:10:11,270 --> 00:10:11,980
Is today not the day

121
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:13,250
