124
00:10:16,980 --> 00:10:17,550
[Li Huayuan, Yellow Maple Valley]

125
00:10:17,550 --> 00:10:18,420
Of course.

126
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:20,730
But you know the rules

127
00:10:20,870 --> 00:10:22,250
