128
00:10:22,510 --> 00:10:24,740
When it is time for new disciples to enter,

129
00:10:24,740 --> 00:10:26,010
I open betting pools.

130
00:10:26,750 --> 00:10:29,580
It helps liven things up, you know?

131
00:10:30,040 --> 00:10:32,750
Of course. Absolutely.

132
00:10:32,750 --> 00:10:34,180
You came at the right time.

133
00:10:36,510 --> 00:10:37,460
The first round

134
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,220
