135
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:40,650
Great!

136
00:10:42,960 --> 00:10:43,730
Left is odd.

137
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:46,980
Right is even.

138
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:48,700
Place your bets. No changes after this.

139
00:10:48,720 --> 00:10:49,300
Come on.

140
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:50,610
A hundred-year lingzhi.

141
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:51,730
I bet on odd.

142
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:52,980
Odd for me too.

143
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:54,610
Me too.

144
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:55,770
I bet on even.

145
00:10:56,910 --> 00:10:57,300
Here.

146
00:11:00,120 --> 00:11:01,300
