147
00:11:01,510 --> 00:11:02,100
Show us the results.

148
00:11:05,080 --> 00:11:05,650
One.

149
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:06,610
Two.

150
00:11:06,910 --> 00:11:07,650
Five.

151
00:11:07,870 --> 00:11:08,490
Six.

152
00:11:08,870 --> 00:11:09,490
Seven.

153
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:10,610
Eight.

154
00:11:11,030 --> 00:11:12,010
16.

155
00:11:13,510 --> 00:11:14,250
16 is even, right?

156
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:15,250
Is 16 even?

157
00:11:15,390 --> 00:11:15,980
Yes, Grandmaster.

158
00:11:16,030 --> 00:11:17,010
It is even!

159
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:17,650
Collect them!

160
00:11:18,600 --> 00:11:19,370
Collect them all!

161
00:11:19,670 --> 00:11:20,580
My talisman!

162
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:22,100
Take them.

163
00:11:22,120 --> 00:11:22,890
What's all the fuss about?

164
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:25,100
There are wins and losses

165
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:26,580
