166
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:27,100
That's right.

167
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:28,220
Accept your loss.

168
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:28,650
Don't be a sore loser.

169
00:11:28,670 --> 00:11:29,180
Good.

170
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:30,010
Huayuan,

171
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:30,850
boys,

172
00:11:31,150 --> 00:11:31,530
we will end here

173
00:11:31,670 --> 00:11:32,300
for today.

174
00:11:32,510 --> 00:11:33,370
I bid you goodbye.

175
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:34,890
Mentor Fu Yunzi.

176
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:35,730
Liu.

177
00:11:36,600 --> 00:11:37,010
Master,

178
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:38,340
I have something important to report.

179
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:40,060
What is it?

180
00:11:40,390 --> 00:11:41,190
A young man holding

181
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:42,460
an Ascension Token has arrived in the valley.

182
00:11:43,790 --> 00:11:44,460
Ascension Token?

183
00:11:45,460 --> 00:11:46,910
[Token]

184
00:11:46,910 --> 00:11:48,700
I haven't seen this thing in over 400 or 500 years.

185
00:11:48,720 --> 00:11:49,370
Indeed.

186
00:11:50,510 --> 00:11:52,060
This is a rare item.

187
00:11:52,390 --> 00:11:52,940
Indeed.

188
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:53,610
This...

189
00:11:57,550 --> 00:11:58,130
Wait a minute.

190
00:11:59,030 --> 00:12:00,180
How many were there just now?

191
00:12:00,270 --> 00:12:01,460
- 16. - 16.

192
00:12:01,630 --> 00:12:02,460
Add this one

193
00:12:02,550 --> 00:12:02,890
and...

194
00:12:05,030 --> 00:12:06,010
What's

195
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:06,770
16 plus 1?

196
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:08,850
18.

197
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:10,980
Fu Yunzi.

198
00:12:11,320 --> 00:12:12,300
I have seen cheating,

199
00:12:12,320 --> 00:12:13,490
