200
00:12:13,510 --> 00:12:14,580
Isn't it 18?

201
00:12:14,600 --> 00:12:15,730
It's 17!

202
00:12:15,850 --> 00:12:17,220
Give me that!

203
00:12:17,670 --> 00:12:18,060
Get it!

204
00:12:18,120 --> 00:12:18,890
Hurry!

205
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:19,370
Quickly!

206
00:12:19,790 --> 00:12:20,770
Whose is this?

207
00:12:20,790 --> 00:12:22,100
- Oh, you. - My talisman!

208
00:12:22,630 --> 00:12:23,490
This token

209
00:12:23,670 --> 00:12:24,820
couldn't have come at a better time.

210
00:12:25,510 --> 00:12:26,490
I'll remember you.

211
00:12:26,750 --> 00:12:27,850
This is yours.

212
00:12:27,870 --> 00:12:28,580
Hold up.

213
00:12:28,910 --> 00:12:29,580
My talisman.

214
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:30,580
Where is he?

215
00:12:31,200 --> 00:12:32,010
At the bottom of the north valley.

216
00:12:52,510 --> 00:12:53,060
Mentor.

217
00:12:53,390 --> 00:12:53,940
What precious possessions

218
00:12:54,270 --> 00:12:55,250
