Snow Mountain Ice Lotus.

221
00:12:59,600 --> 00:13:01,610
Paired with hundred-year banana leaf you brought,

222
00:13:01,870 --> 00:13:02,940
it balances cold and heat.

223
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:03,730
Nourishes the spirit root.

224
00:13:04,720 --> 00:13:05,180
Excellent.

225
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:06,890
Wu.

226
00:13:07,440 --> 00:13:08,250
