229
00:13:15,630 --> 00:13:16,490
That's a fine item.

230
00:13:16,550 --> 00:13:17,610
Nine Heavens Mystic Cicada.

231
00:13:18,270 --> 00:13:19,300
Gentlest of all.

232
00:13:20,550 --> 00:13:21,300
Please.

233
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:25,180
