234
00:13:28,630 --> 00:13:29,530
Let's enjoy some fine tea.

235
00:13:34,360 --> 00:13:34,850
Allow me.

236
00:13:35,750 --> 00:13:36,250
Watch this.

237
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:44,010
Excellent tea.

238
00:13:45,790 --> 00:13:46,300
Enjoy.

239
00:13:52,510 --> 00:13:53,220
