240
00:13:54,550 --> 00:13:55,580
Here comes the tea moocher.

241
00:13:55,720 --> 00:13:56,460
Quick! Finish the tea!

242
00:14:00,390 --> 00:14:02,010
I hope the tea scalds you,

243
00:14:02,030 --> 00:14:03,370
