245
00:14:06,360 --> 00:14:06,650
Look.

246
00:14:07,960 --> 00:14:09,700
I brought something.

247
00:14:10,360 --> 00:14:11,280
A hundred-year spirit herb.

248
00:14:11,840 --> 00:14:12,730
Excellent choice.

249
00:14:15,750 --> 00:14:16,340
Hongfu,

250
00:14:16,670 --> 00:14:17,730
I brought it just for you.

251
00:14:19,750 --> 00:14:20,300
Everyone,

252
00:14:21,240 --> 00:14:23,920
today Yellow Maple Valley welcomes a rare guest,

253
00:14:24,080 --> 00:14:26,100
someone who's the likes of whom we haven't encountered in a hundred years.

254
00:14:26,750 --> 00:14:27,060
Come

255
00:14:27,360 --> 00:14:27,890
and have a look at this.

256
00:14:28,030 --> 00:14:28,460
What is it?

257
00:14:33,120 --> 00:14:34,610
I'm Song Meng, a Foundation Establishment disciple

258
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:35,250
of Yellow Maple Valley.

259
00:14:35,550 --> 00:14:36,490
This is my sixth junior brother,

260
00:14:36,600 --> 00:14:37,060
Wu Xuan,

261
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:38,060
