263
00:14:40,440 --> 00:14:41,130
That is right.

264
00:14:45,150 --> 00:14:45,650
What is your name?

265
00:14:47,960 --> 00:14:48,820
My name is Han Li.

266
00:14:52,320 --> 00:14:53,300
Why is he here?

267
00:14:54,960 --> 00:14:56,310
That guy has

268
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:57,960
the Ascension Token?

269
00:14:58,320 --> 00:14:59,420
That guy?

270
00:15:00,200 --> 00:15:00,830
No way.

271
00:15:01,790 --> 00:15:02,970
